OL,5,G0015 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FNorway v Senegal (Kick-off
OL,7,     F1.00am). Laura Woods presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the second match in
OL,9,     FGroup I for both teams, held at
OL,10,     FNew York/New Jersey Stadium in the
OL,11,     FUSA. Norway were in outstanding
OL,12,     Fform in qualifying, winning all
OL,13,     Feight of their matches to top a
OL,14,     Fgroup containing the likes of
OL,15,     FItaly and Israel, with Manchester
OL,16,     FCity star Erling Haaland scoring
OL,17,     Fan incredible 16 goals. However,
OL,18,     Fthey face a tough test against the
OL,19,     FSenegalese, who reached the last
OL,20,     F16 in 2022, losing out to England
OL,21,     Fin a 3-0 defeat. The African side
OL,22,     Flost their opening match of this
